# API Layer

## Organization
- API logic is located in [src/api/](mdc:src/api).
- Each API file corresponds to a feature or resource (e.g., [auth.api.ts](mdc:src/api/auth.api.ts), [match.api.ts](mdc:src/api/match.api.ts)).
- [api.base.ts](mdc:src/api/api.base.ts) provides shared API logic and base configuration.

## Conventions
- Use Axios for HTTP requests.
- Export functions for each API endpoint.
- Group related endpoints in the same file.

## Example
- [auth.api.ts](mdc:src/api/auth.api.ts): Authentication-related API calls.
- [match.api.ts](mdc:src/api/match.api.ts): Match-related API calls.
